NK005(ca)002:0: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi bla brgyud gsol 'debs ni /
NK005(ca)002:1: kun bzang rigs lnga gsang bdag dri med grags //
NK005(ca)002:2: in+d+ra b+hu ti u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK005(ca)002:3: ku ku r+au dza mu di ta rnams la //
NK005(ca)002:4: gsol ba 'debs so mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)002:5: arka so ma badz+ra ba hu ta //
NK005(ca)002:6: mus to ba hu tahdang gus ko ta //
NK005(ca)002:7: dri med bshes gnyen rma lo rin mchog la //
NK005(ca)002:8: gsol ba mkhas pa'i dbang po gtsug gyer rnam gnyis dang //
NK005(ca)002:9: tshul khrims byang chub thugs sras rnam pa gsum //
NK005(ca)002:10: cog ro rgyal ba'i yon tan /
NK005(ca)002:12: rdo rje 'jam dpal dang gsum mo //
NK005(ca)002:14: byang chub 'od dang blo gros rgyal mtshan la //
NK005(ca)002:15: gsol ba rin chen tshul khrims rong ston chos bzang dang //
NK005(ca)002:16: yam shud blo bzang 'gos ston zla ba 'bar //
NK005(ca)002:17: zla ba 'bum grags dngos grub rgyal mtshan la /
NK005(ca)002:18: gsol ba 'gos ston chos rdor 'gos pa dngos grub mgon //
NK005(ca)002:19: dbus pa sangs 'bum gser steng chos 'od bzang //
NK005(ca)002:20: mi bskyod rdo rje mkhan chen bsod 'phel la //
NK005(ca)002:21: gsol ba bag ston tshul rgyal bla chen bsod nams dpal //
NK005(ca)002:22: 'jam dbyangs kun blo nam mkha' tshul khrims dang //
NK005(ca)002:23: rong pa blo bzang mkhyen rab chos rje la //
NK005(ca)002:24: gsol ba sam b+ha sh+r+ai tshul khrims 'od zer 'bar //
NK005(ca)002:25: bsod nams dpal 'byor rin chen bkra shis sde //
NK005(ca)002:26: blo gsal rgya mtsho 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse la //
NK005(ca)002:27: gsol ba dbang phyug rab brtan bsod nams mchog ldan dpal //
NK005(ca)002:28: ngag dbang o rgyan rig 'dzin gter bdag gling //
NK005(ca)002:29: 'gyur med rgya mtsho rin chen rnam rgyal la //
NK005(ca)002:30: gsol ba o rgyan bstan 'dzin phrin las rnam par rgyal //
NK005(ca)002:31: phrin las chos sgron sangs rgyas kun dag'i zhabs //
NK005(ca)002:32: bstan 'dzin nor bu phan bde'i 'od zer la //
NK005(ca)002:33: gsol ba brgyud srol kun 'dus rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK005(ca)002:34: bde gshegs sgyu ma bde mchog yi dam lha //
NK005(ca)002:35: ma sring mkha' 'gro dam can rgya mtsho la //
NK005(ca)002:36: gsol ba rig 'dzin bla ma lha dang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)002:37: 'bral med yid la rtse gcig bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK005(ca)002:38: rigs lnga'i bde gshegs bsnyen pa yongs rdzogs nas //
NK005(ca)002:39: he ru ka dpal mngon du 'grub par shog /
NK005(ca)002:40: ces rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas kyis mdzad pa'i
NK005(ca)002:41: brgyud 'debs la brgyud pa'i khyad par gyis rgyal sras
NK005(ca)002:42: rin chen rnam rgyal nas bdag gi rigs bdag 'gyur
NK005(ca)002:43: med phan bde'i 'od zer bar kha bsgyur ba po
